| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3106 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8b0bb569-2f3f-5915-89ba-727f007da0d0"
